{"tid":2362123,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"試當真の許腎粉絲的自我修養","createTime":"2021-01-11T08:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T21:34:34.000Z","uid":114400,"like":13,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"24f54e5027eff9dff78f286d3b5197c8dd61f0e2","tid":2362123,"uid":114400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"大家好 <br />\n我係上個月因為試當真<br />\n而成為許賢&middot;死忠&middot;四週目的普通市民一名<br />\n所以近來一直返睇腎哥哥以前d片<br />\nCaptv到金剛crew 依家仲努力睇緊 未睇曬<br />\n最近都係因為佢地睇多左youtube<br />\n係我依家有follow開3隻手指數得曬嘅youtube爸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似呢集<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qyeo1Ob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyeo1Ob.png&h=c84f1bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢集<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxRe8tQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxRe8tQ.png&h=ccf46460&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAGiQHc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAGiQHc.png&h=6ed6b42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同呢集咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JUcU81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JUcU81.png&h=d923b0c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然當時都有睇下captv 但冇留意到佢地<br />\n一開始我內心有點兒震驚<br />\n原來小腎以前嘅髮型係咁樣架....<br />\n..嗯.....好啦...真係令我大開眼界<br />\n <br />\n因為作為現役腎仔死忠嘅自覺<br />\n我都好積極努力接受<br />\n果然每個人都有特別嘅品味<br />\n依家當我愈睇愈多佢地以前嘅片嘅時候<br />\n法國腎仔嘅髮型係我眼中都愈黎愈順眼<br />\n但<br />\n正當我站在離心理關口外1cm的距離<br />\n下一秒就能突破的距離<br />\n冇錯 當你睇到呢到 <br />\n其實這一秒已經突破左心理關口的我<br />\n發現<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AZ8tyn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AZ8tyn.png&h=a405e04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AcU8yo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AcU8yo.png&h=357285d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpASVdq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpASVdq.png&h=ced78395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啊<br />\n啊啊啊啊<br />\n啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊<br />\n假髮？？？<br />\nへえええ( &ordm;＿&ordm; )(((;꒪ꈊ꒪;)))<br />\n原來係假髮黎架！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n&Sigma;(-`Д&acute;-<br />\n我真係唔知啊媽咪！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都有諗過架！！<br />\n心諗 點解會有人留個咁嘅髮型！！<br />\n真係好奇怪！！-&gt;新鮮-&gt;正常-&gt;順眼！<br />\n <br />\n咁我見佢好似條條片都係咁嘅髮型<br />\n又好似唔識甩咁<br />\n就以為真係有人會留個咁嘅髮型 當係自己見識少<br />\n啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！！！！<br />\n我真係努力左架 <br />\n但係你依家話我知.....原來係假髮！！！！<br />\n邊有人帶假髮唔話俾人知架！！！<br />\n唔得 我要去冷靜下先<br />\n陣間等我嘗試下返番個關口裡面....<br />\n冇咩事我都係出返去先 打擾了！<br />\n<br />\n以上<br />\n腎哥哥的小粉絲 筆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5339ee359ae553275dd59b2fe84df60ca01e2b","tid":2362123,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"感謝投稿"},{"pid":"1a3874af64c8ec6e050543f3ca18583913a7ee9c","tid":2362123,"uid":384207,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"hi 豪哥"},{"pid":"550fbd51fa6ded25a987c3282ce3a4c7987372b3","tid":2362123,"uid":114400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"啊 我知我好on9 <br />\n不過唔係要投稿係真人真事<br />\n啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e52599b893b514940acc341cdf323b7d209580a","tid":2362123,"uid":227597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:48:59.000Z","msg":"我都唔知<im